.text-wrapper
  .inner
    %p
      We where ready to refine our ideas and test them with our target audience.
      We built a low fidelity prototype, recruited testers and used Google
      Hangouts to facilitate the test. By sharing a link to a .jpg of our
      prototype and using the screen-sharing functionality we where able to make
      observations and ask questions while the tester remains in their
      environment.

